{"tid":2235012,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女團Stellar被騙拍「丁字褲照」！成員曝超扯內幕：原本說太色了不會用","createTime":"2020-10-08T10:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T07:51:24.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5296be692d1fe5bbc6469c89704e3986716faedc","tid":2235012,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:42:45.000Z","msg":"[img]南韓新韓綜《Miss Back》邀請逐漸被大眾遺忘的偶像出身女歌手上節目，其中曾以「限制級女團」Stellar出道的佳英透露辛酸故事，原來她們是拍攝MV當天才知道要穿露骨服裝，就算表達了強烈意願不想穿，卻「被騙拍照」後刊登出來，讓現場主持人大罵髒話。<br />\n[/img]<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5193/d5193123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5193%2Fd5193123.jpg&h=1d743619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女團Stellar當年其實是被騙拍下「丁字褲照」。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／MBN Entertainment）<br />\n<br />\n《Miss Back》即將在今（8日）晚間首播，在最新釋出的預告片中，佳英談到2015年推出歌曲《Vibrato》的爭議宣傳照，當時她們穿上緊身洋裝，但裙子一角卻從及膝處開岔到腰部，且讓她們穿上了丁字褲，讓細細的繩子露出，當時被批過於色情，根本不是偶像該穿的服裝。<br />\n<br />\n佳英在節目上首次透露背後超扯內幕，「我們先試好裝了，都到了拍攝MV現場，突然要求我們換裝。」看到超露的服裝當下，成員有表達沒辦法穿這套，但公司卻說，「為什麼還沒穿就說無法穿？不然先拍拍看，要是真的覺得太色情我們就換掉，太奇怪我們就不使用，會刪掉。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5193/d5193125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5193%2Fd5193125.jpg&h=db1b3f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女團Stellar前成員佳英還原當時拍攝過程。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／MBN Entertainment）<br />\n<br />\n被迫穿上超露服裝的成員，只能暫時妥協，然而事情根本不是她們所想，佳英對大家說，「當天真的只拍了5張，公司的人看完說真的太色了，要我們去換別套，然而最後這樣的照片卻公開了。」節目擔任製作人與心靈導師的女歌手白智榮聽到，摀著嘴憤怒飆罵，宋恩伊也火大說，「怎麼可以做出這種事情」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5193/d5193124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5193%2Fd5193124.jpg&h=17b13f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲白智榮與其他在場人員聽了都相當憤怒。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／MBN Entertainment）<br />\n<br />\n女團Stellar 2011年以4人女團出道，但到2018年解散前共有8名成員曾離開或加入，佳英是元老成員。出道前2年原本走清純形象卻不紅，2013年突然改穿性感服裝後雖有討論度，但卻淪為「限制級女團」，節目上佳英也說經常會收到網友私訊「生殖器」照片，讓她不堪其擾。<br />\n<br />\n《Miss Back》節目班底還找來T-ara朴昭妍、Crayon Pop昭燏、After School Raina、Dal★Shabet秀彬、WA$$UP Nada、Nine Muses世羅、THE ARK有珍等，都曾是KPOP粉絲熟悉的女偶像。<br />\n<br />\n▼《Miss Back》節目預告。（影片來源：YouTube MBN Entertainment）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tt_D0yaWDSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTt_D0yaWDSw&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=fd72940c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tt_D0yaWDSw</a>"},{"pid":"f51265719b63030122d85873aa068138b85ea61a","tid":2235012,"uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/8d/4d/c6/8d4dc63e16ad10d4c76819e7a3373475.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F8d%2F4d%2Fc6%2F8d4dc63e16ad10d4c76819e7a3373475.gif&h=a7d34f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/2qol.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2F2qol.gif&h=4f0a1c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ryrky7T67yM/V3JgNBTfC2I/AAAAAAAAXac/dObXgiG8LFgZV6h4N2F9S_QtC4w7RNIQACLcB/s640/minhee_9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ryrky7T67yM%2FV3JgNBTfC2I%2FAAAAAAAAXac%2FdObXgiG8LFgZV6h4N2F9S_QtC4w7RNIQACLcB%2Fs640%2Fminhee_9.gif&h=bcdc9719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ifunny.co/images/e252ba3e890c16183c4ce45d98f0351b8fc332de4fb34d0348a77f7df49698d4_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ifunny.co%2Fimages%2Fe252ba3e890c16183c4ce45d98f0351b8fc332de4fb34d0348a77f7df49698d4_1.gif&h=a7f93fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n少數會J既霉團<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187c3ebba99fab041fba7e8e7f5bd096cb8a726a","tid":2235012,"uid":48783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f51265719b63030122d85873aa068138b85ea61a","tid":2235012,"uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTi